BT 1 0 0 1 0 13.9805 Tm 7.875 TL /F1 5.25 Tf 0 0 0 rg (Basic functionality of Netconf is simply achieved via using ) Tj /F4 5.25 Tf (netconf-yang) Tj /F1 5.25 Tf ( command. However the great benefit of netconf comes with using validation and rollback, which is a feature in DB world as) Tj T* (ATOMIC operations. Either all-or-nothing. This can be achieved by netconf using the datastore. Furthermore an ACL should be applied to restrict connectivity to the management Hosts.) Tj T* ET
